detailedDescription.articleBody:
Hélder Jorge Leal Rodrigues Barbosa is a Portuguese professional footballer who plays as a left winger for Turkish club Akhisar Belediyespor.
He amassed Primeira Liga totals of 148 matches and 19 goals, mainly for Braga and Académica. He also played for teams in Spain, Greece, the United Arab Emirates and Turkey.
All youth levels comprised, Barbosa won 77 caps for Portugal. He made his senior debut in 2012.
